Former Eskom Board chairperson, Zola Tsotsi is expected to give Eskom-related evidence again at the State Capture Commission this morning. Editor's note: Livestream courtesy #DStv403 #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Former Eskom Board Chairperson, Zola Tsotsi is appearing at the State Capture Commission. During his testimony last year, he alleged the Guptas wanted the exclusive right to supply gas through Eskom units in the Western Cape.